Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This class is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:24.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... what are you ta—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I died without accomplishing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:31.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what’s the point of doing all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:37.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take me to heaven if I score well on tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:39.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:53.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, it’s the student council president...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:54.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s going to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then quit complaining and do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:07.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you need to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:09.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How will you accomplish it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:11.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, what do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people needed courage to face their past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:26.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people needed strength to reach their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:30.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people needed time and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:34.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:36.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:39.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the courage to face you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:42.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:44.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:46.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:52.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever feel unreasonable resentment or hesitation, come to the student council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be waiting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he’s cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never seen anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have a girlfriend??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:08.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he's waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You too. Sit down!
